{"type":"answer","id":12604,"parentType":"question","parentId":2621,"uid":1967,"contents":"貌似是貼URL,如果你要發的圖在線上的話那麼右鍵點擊然後點擊“複製連結網址”，然後在品蔥的發言編輯框內點擊那個看起來像圖片的按鈕（或者是那個像回形針的按鈕）並將網址黏貼進去即可<br>\n至於本地的圖怎麼發我暫時不太清楚...或許可以先把圖上傳到網上然後再複製連結網址吧<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://external-preview.redd.it/S1Hwl72jrGo8gH440Ke1jwVKwrt4gCkiErS48M3flZ0.png?auto=webp&amp;s=703duntrusted fake 2049bbs32cc5b640ade453cf809a7ccecc</a>&nbsp;圖片按鈕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\" url=\"\" link=\"\" ahr0chm6ly9lehrlcm5hbc1wcmv2awv3lnjlzgquaxqvuzfid2w3mmpyr284z0g0ndblztfqd1zld3j0ngdda2lfclm0oe0zzmxamc5wbmc_yxv0bz13zwjwjnm9nzazzdiwn2rhywnlztmyy2m1yjy0mgfkztq1m2nmoda5ytdjy2vjyw\"=\"\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n\n</a><div class=\"meta clearfix\"><a href=\"https://external-preview.redd.it/S1Hwl72jrGo8gH440Ke1jwVKwrt4gCkiErS48M3flZ0.png?auto=webp&amp;s=703duntrusted fake 2049bbs32cc5b640ade453cf809a7ccecc</a>&nbsp;圖片按鈕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\" url=\"\" link=\"\" ahr0chm6ly9lehrlcm5hbc1wcmv2awv3lnjlzgquaxqvuzfid2w3mmpyr284z0g0ndblztfqd1zld3j0ngdda2lfclm0oe0zzmxamc5wbmc_yxv0bz13zwjwjnm9nzazzdiwn2rhywnlztmyy2m1yjy0mgfkztq1m2nmoda5ytdjy2vjyw\"=\"\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n<span class=\"aw-small-text pull-right\">2019-03-12</span>\n\n<span class=\"operate aw-vote-ui\">\n</span></a><a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"agree disabled\">\n<i class=\"icon icon-agree\"></i> <b class=\"count\">1</b>\n</a>\n\n\n<span class=\"operate\">\n<a href=\"javascript:;\" onclick=\"toggle_disscusion($(this));\" class=\"aw-add-comment\" data-id=\"12604\" data-type=\"answer\" data-comment-count=\"0\"><i class=\"icon icon-comment\"></i> 0</a>\n</span>\n\n<div class=\"more-operate\">\n<a href=\"/vote/log/item_type-answer__item_id-12604\" class=\"aw-small-text\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"icon icon-users\"></i></a>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"aw-comment-box\" style=\"display:none\">\n<div class=\"aw-comment-list\"></div>\n\n<a class=\"aw-load-more-content\">\n<span>更多</span>\n</a>\n\n<p align=\"center\">该主题目前已经被锁定, 无法添加新回复</p>\n</d